	Caring Clooney    
	 London, July 10 (PTI): Actor George Clooney is planning to shoot his upcoming film in LAquila, Italy, which was hit by an earthquake recently.       
	The actor hopes that the film project will help revive the areas economy and bring some cheer to the local people.       
	The actor, who owns a vacation home on the banks of Lake Como in Italy, visited the Italian city yesterday and thrilled locals with his film news. Well shoot a film here at the end of September, in which I will act, said Clooney. He also met people whose homes were destroyed by the quake.                                                                                                                                                                        
